item.description: Join Anne Deidre, the Intuitive Millionaire Coach, as she introduces herself, her talents and shares the keys that have allowed her to make over her own life, overcome depression and anxiety, and change the lives of thousands of her coaching clients. In "Extreme Intuitive Makeover - 55 Keys to Health, Wealth and Happiness," Anne leads you to your own inner brilliance with unlocking exercises that calm your mind and reignite your dreams, passion, and purpose. Anne will also offer Oracle Card Readings from her Spiritual Enlightenment Oracle Cards which she created and personally illustrated! The Spiritual Enlightenment Oracle Cards - A Toolkit for Creating Divine Magic and Miracles in Your Life are spiritually encoded to effortlessly expand your consciousness and activate higher levels of awareness within you. Don't miss out!
